Package com.terturl.MMO.MMOEntity.ResourcePack

Class MobBoneFile

java.lang.Object
com.terturl.MMO.MMOEntity.ResourcePack.MobBoneFile
public class MobBoneFile extends Object
This will create a saddle.json file that will hold the information of how to create a new model of each body part a MMOMob will contain. This will contain all textures needed to create the mob visually and all locations of the mob's cubes
